# Download Android source with local_manifests
 Refer to http://source.android.com/source/downloading.html

 $ repo init -u https://android.googlesource.com/platform/manifest -b android-11.0.0_r17
 $ git clone https://github.com/PontusPersson/local_manifests .repo/local_manifests -b arpi-11
 $ repo sync

# Build for Raspberry Pi 4
 https://github.com/PontusPersson/device_arpi_rpi4

Use -j[n] option on sync & build steps, if build host has a good number of CPU cores.
